OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan gambles away huge      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faccidental Covid payment in
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FJapan                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A 24-year-old man who was mistakenly   
OL,6, paid millions of Japanese yen has      
OL,7, already lost the money through online  
OL,8, gambling, his lawyer says.             
OL,10,FThe man received 46.3m yen ($357,400;  
OL,11,F#287,000) in his bank account - money  
OL,12,Ffrom a Covid relief fund that was      
OL,13,Fsupposed to be shared among 463 people.
OL,15,FHe initially said he would co-operate  
OL,16,Fwith officials, but has since vanished.
OL,18,FThe southern town of Abu in Japan's    
OL,19,FYamaguchi Prefecture is suing the man  
OL,20,Fand also considering criminal action.  
